login-scenarios.py:

positive test  : valid username and  password
open browser
go to website
go to login page
enter username(......)
enter password(......)
click_login()
verify it opens welcome page.

negative test : invalid username
open browser
go to website
go to login page
enter username(invalid)
enter password(......)
click_login()
assert 'Invalid email address' == get.error_msg()

negative test : invalid  password
